"┊ LINSTOR3 ┊ SATELLITE ┊ 172.16.16.113:3366 (PLAIN) ┊ Online ┊\n"
"╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n"
msgstr ""
"# linstor node list\n"
"╭────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n"
"┊ Node     ┊ NodeType  ┊ Addresses                  ┊ State  ┊\n"
"╞════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╡\n"
"┊ LINSTOR1 ┊ COMBINED  ┊ 172.16.16.111:3366 (PLAIN) ┊ Online ┊\n"
"┊ LINSTOR2 ┊ SATELLITE ┊ 172.16.16.112:3366 (PLAIN) ┊ Online ┊\n"
"┊ LINSTOR3 ┊ SATELLITE ┊ 172.16.16.113:3366 (PLAIN) ┊ Online ┊\n"
"╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Verify that the output from a LINSTOR storage pool list command includes an "
"LVM or ZFS backed storage pool:"
msgstr ""
"LINSTORのストレージプールリストコマンドの出力にLVMまたはZFSでバックアップされ"
"たストレージプールが含まれることを確認してください。"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# linstor storage-pool list\n"
"╭─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[...]─────────╮\n"
